# Vision Motors - E-commerce Website

## Overview
Vision Motors is a fully responsive e-commerce website designed for selling luxury cars, pre-used cars, and motorcycles. The platform provides an intuitive user interface, allowing customers to browse products, view detailed descriptions, add items to the cart, and proceed to checkout.

## Project Structure
```
/ecom-website
│── /Cart
│   │── cart.html
│   │── cart.css
│   │── cart.js
│
│── /Product
│   │── product.html
│   │── product.css
│   │── product.js
│   │── product-detail.html
│   │── product-detail.css
│   │── product-detail.js
│
│── /images (Contains all product images)
│
│── e-shop.html (Homepage)
│── style.css (Global Stylesheet)
│── script.js (Global JavaScript)
```

## Features
- **Home Page:** Displays a hero section with a call-to-action button and a product listing.
- **Product Page:** Showcases all available products with filtering options.
- **Product Details Page:** Displays detailed information about each product, including pricing, tax information, and additional images.
- **Cart Page:** Allows users to view, add, remove items, and see the total cost.
- **Local Storage Integration:** The shopping cart is stored in the browser’s local storage for persistence.

